Title: Distance Formula for Grassmann Manifold --Applied to Anandan--Aharonov
  Type Uncertainty Relation--
Authors: Minoru Hirayama, Takeshi Hamada and Jin Chen
Comments: 25pages, LaTex file , TOYAMA-80, KANAZAWA-94-21
Journal-ref: Prog.Theor.Phys. 93 (1995) 255-272
\\
  The time-energy uncertainty relation of Anandan-Aharonov is generalized to a
relation involving a set of quantum state vectors. This is achieved by
obtaining an explicit formula for the distance between two finitely separated
points in the Grassmann manifold.
